Who's to say we havent gotten bad players from the transfers?  After all, most of the server never even views these boards.  (Believe it or not, people get trained, are ks'ed, are stalked, and made fun of for RP and sometimes... it isnt heard about here! &lt;gasp&gt;)  And even if we havent seen poor players transfering here, why risk it?<br>
