 not only good at their class, but elemental flagged, thus saving us a whole hell of alot of time and making it easier on everyone. i'm all for recruiting from this server, but having that extra option for recruitment in cross server transfers makes it easier on us.  <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://img.ranchoweb.com/images/cathead/fairy_bounce02.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
